### Create a charge
POST http://localhost:8080/charges
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idempotencyKey": "key-001",
  "amount": 99.99,
  "currency": "USD",
  "customerEmail": "customer@example.com",
  "cardToken": "tok_visa",
  "description": "Test charge"
}

### List latest charges
GET http://localhost:8080/charges

### Get charge by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/charges/{{chargeId}}

### Search customers by email
GET http://localhost:8080/customers/search?email=customer@example.com

### Render support message
POST http://localhost:8080/support/render-message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "John Doe"
}
